{"arkId":"cl010094812","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010094812","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"La Marne","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"La Marne"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1703 - 1706","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [SCULPT] Salle 102 - Cour Marly, Salle 102 - Partie m\u00e9diane","room":"Salle 102, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau -1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1703,"endYear":1706,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIIe si\u00e8cle - d\u00e9but du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Coysevox, Antoine","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1720","place":"","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1640","place":"Lyon","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q505134"},{"label":"France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 3007","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"groupe","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"2,16","displayDimension":"2,16 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"1,3","displayDimension":"1,3 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,845","displayDimension":"0,845 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"marbre","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"parc (France-\u003EMarly) (haut de la Rivi\u00e8re)","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Un des quatre groupes command\u00e9s en 1698 par Jules Hardouin-Mansart (1646-1708), surintendant des B\u00e2timents du roi, pour la Rivi\u00e8re du parc de Marly, avec La Seine (MR 1825), Neptune (RF 3006) et Amphitrite (RF 3005). Mod\u00e8les ex\u00e9cut\u00e9s en 1698-1699. Moulage des mod\u00e8les en pl\u00e2tre ex\u00e9cut\u00e9 en 1699 sur les emplacements pr\u00e9vus pour les marbres. Ex\u00e9cution commenc\u00e9e une fois termin\u00e9s le Mercure et La Renomm\u00e9e (MR 1822 et MR 1824), et ex\u00e9cut\u00e9s en marbre de 1703 \u00e0 1708 (d\u0027apr\u00e8s l\u0027inventaires des collections royales de 1707, ex\u00e9cut\u00e9s en 1705). Parfait paiement, 18 avril 1712. \r\nD\u00e9pos\u00e9 \u00e0 la ville de Brest et affect\u00e9 au d\u00e9cor de la fontaine de Neptune sur le cours Dajot, apr\u00e8s septembre 1801 (Rivi\u00e8re qui f\u00e9conde la terre et provoque la v\u00e9g\u00e9tation). Class\u00e9 monument historique par arr\u00eat\u00e9 du 15 mai 1909. Abrit\u00e9 au ch\u00e2teau de Kerjean (Nord-Finist\u00e8re) de 1940 \u00e0 1953, puis entrepos\u00e9 au ch\u00e2teau de Champs-sur-Marne (Seine-et-Marne). Vers\u00e9 au Louvre le 27 septembre 1966 et inventori\u00e9 pour r\u00e9gularisation en 1971.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"versement","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1801","startYear":1801,"endYear":1801},{"type":"date d\u0027arriv\u00e9e au Mus\u00e9e","value":"27\/09\/1966","startYear":1966,"endYear":1966},{"type":"date de l\u0027inscription sur l\u0027inventaire","value":"1971","startYear":1971,"endYear":1971}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"valu